Upgrade wizard
==============

Change plugin to regular content element

FlexForm to regular tt_content fields:

sDEF - pages => storage_folder
sDEF - template_file => REMOVED

sMAIL - YNemail => survey_mail_send_type
sMAIL - Subject => survey_mail_subject
sMAIL - FromEmail => survey_mail_from_address
sMAIL - FromName => survey_mail_from_name
sMAIL - ToEmail => survey_mail_to
sMAIL - CcEmail => survey_mail_cc
sMAIL - MessageBox => survey_mail_body

sACCESS - captcha => survey_captcha
sACCESS - access_level => survey_access_level
sACCESS - entering_stage => survey_entering_stage
sACCESS - anonymous_mode => survey_anonymous_mode
sACCESS - cookie_lifetime => survey_cookie_lifetime

sCOMPLETION - completion_action => survey_completion_action
sCOMPLETION - completion_url => survey_completion_page
sCOMPLETION - close_button => survey_completion_close_button
sCOMPLETION - continue_button => survey_completion_continue_button

sNAVIGATION - navigation_back => survey_navigation_back
sNAVIGATION - navigation_cancel => survey_navigation_cancel
sNAVIGATION - cancel_url => survey_cancel_page

sNUMBERING - page_numbering => survey_numbering_page
sNUMBERING - question_numbering => survey_numbering_question

sSCORING => This is a sheet with sections
These sections need to be transformed to tx_survey_score records and attached to the survey_scoring field

sOTHER - maximum_responses => survey_maximum_responses
sOTHER - responses_per_user => survey_responses_per_user
sOTHER - days_for_update => survey_days_for_update
sOTHER - validation => survey_validation
sOTHER - first_column_width => survey_first_column_width

Icons
=====

Design new icons for the CType (+ New Content Element Wizard), score, item, answer and result

tx_pbsurvey_item
================

Field changes

answers - Changed to IRRE
conditions => condition_groups - Changed to IRRE
rows - Changed to IRRE
image - Changed to IRRE
images - Changed to IRRE

answers_allow_additional => answers_additional_allow
answers_text_additional => answers_additional_text
answers_type_additional => answers_additional_type

beginning_number => number_start
ending_number => number_end
total_number => number_total

default_date => date_default
maximum_date => date_maximum
minimum_date => date_minimum

default_value_num => value_default_numeric
default_value_tf => value_default_true_false
default_value_txt => value_default_text
default_value_yn => value_default_yes_no

maximum_length => length_maximum

maximum_value => value_maximum
minimum_value => value_minimum

options_maximum_responses => options_responses_maximum
options_minimum_responses => options_responses_minimum
